(236, 33, 'Kovalam - Varkala (70 kms)', '\"After breakfast drive to Varkala. Varkala is an amazing beach destination situated in South kerala at North end border of Trivandrum District, It is also an important Hindu centre of pilgrimage. This beautiful beach destination is been ranked as one of the 10 top seasonal beaches in the world by Discovery channel. On arrival check in to the hotel. Overnight stay at hotel.\r\n\"'),
