(272, 38, 'Bali', '\"After a hearty breakfast, spend the day at leisure.\r\nWith Frills: If you opt for a With Frills package, you are taken to Benoa for water sports in the morning and Tanah Lot at sunset tour in the evening. Today, you will enjoy watersports at Tanjung Benoa. Feel the wind and enjoy the amazing view from the sky with Parasailing. Banana Boat can take up to 5 persons at the same time. Enjoy with your friends and family. Jet Ski means the pleasure of high speeds on the sea. Please ride with the instructor for safety.\r\nAfter you enjoy the water sports, get back to the hotel for a quick change before your proceed for the sunset tour to Tanah Lot.\r\nIn the afternoon, you will be picked up to visit to the sacred Tanah Lot. Temple built on an ocean rock on the exotic west coast of Bali and eyewitness the beautiful sunset in Tanah Lot. Overnight stay at the hotel.\"'),
