(276, 39, 'Bali', '\"After a hearty breakfast, spend the day at leisure.\r\nWith Frills: If you opt for a With Frills package, you will be taken on a full day Barong Kintamani tour. The highlight of this tour is the magnificent view of Mount and Lake Batur with the smoky Agung Volcano in the background. Enroute stops at Singapadu village to see the Barong & Keris dance performance, Celuk the center of gold and silver works, Mas the center of woodcarvings, Ubud the center of Balinese paintings, Goa Gajah (elephant cave) and the holy springs of Tirta Empul at tampaksiring. Then proceed to Kintamani to enjoy the panorama of the semi-active volcano, Mount Batur which stands majestically over the beautiful Batur lake whilst enjoying lunch (vegetarian and non-veg Indonesian).\r\nReturn back to the hotel for an overnight stay.\"'),
(277, 39, 'Bali', '\"After a hearty breakfast, spend the day at leisure.\r\nWith Frills: If you opt for a With Frills package, you are taken to Benoa for water sports in the morning. Enjoy watersports at Tanjung Benoa with an amazing view from the sky with Parasailing. Take Banana Boat ride and also experience the pleasure of high speeds on Jet Ski. Please ride with the instructor for safety.\r\nAfter you enjoy the water sports, get back to the hotel for a quick change before your proceed for the sunset tour to Tanah Lot.\r\nIn the afternoon, you will be picked up to visit to the sacred Tanah Lot. Temple built on an ocean rock on the exotic west coast of Bali and eyewitness the beautiful sunset in Tanah Lot. Overnight stay at the hotel.\"'),
