(772, 176, 'Depart from Kuala Lumpur', 'When in Malaysia, food is something that should be high on the checklist. Enjoy a variety of food and shop till you drop. Visit the Pavillion KL, shop at the Low Yat Plaza or eat at the open-air cafes in Bukit Bintang. As this will be your last day in Kuala Lampur, we suggest that you plan your day according to the time of your flight. Check-out from your hotel as per the hotel policies and get a transfer to the airport. As you board your flight, bid goodbye to the lion city and return safely to your home.'),
