(992, 205, 'Kodaikanal', 'After breakfast proceed for sightseeing tour of Kodaikanal, visit KurinjiAndavar,Bryant\'s park, Pillar Rock, Coaker\'sPark, Green Valley view point, Telescope house, Silent Valley, Star shaped KodaikanalLake & Chittiar Park. Later in the evening transfer to the hotel forovernight stay.'),
