(2250, 363, 'Srinagar - Delhi-Departure', '\"Today after breakfast you will be transferred Srinagar airport time to catch flight for Delhi. On arrival at Delhi airport you will be transferred to Delhi International airport time to catch onward flight.\r\n\"'),
(2251, 364, 'Arrive Delhi :', 'On arrival at Delhi airport, meet our representative who will take you to your pre booked hotel and assist you in checking in process of the hotel. After check in at the hotel, the rest of the day is free for leisure. An overnight stay at hotel.'),
(2252, 364, 'Delhi :', '\"Today, after breakfast we will proceed for full day sightseeing tour of Delhi. We will visit Jama Masjid, Red Fort and Rajghat. We will also drive past to India Gate and President House, Lotus temple, Qutub Minar and Akshardham temple.\r\nLater, return back to the hotel for an overnight stay.\r\n\"'),
(2253, 364, 'Delhi – Agra-Delhi :Taj Mahal', '\"Today, enjoy an early morning breakfast and drive to Agra. On arrival, our representative will meet you and take you for Agra sightseeing tour. We will visit Taj Mahal , Agra Fort and Sikandra. In the evening, we will drive back to Delhi. Enjoy a night stay at the hotel.\r\n\"'),
(2254, 364, 'Delhi - Srinagar:', '\"In the morning after breakfast, we will transfer you to domestic airport to catch the flight for Srinagar. On arrival, our representative will meet and assist you to drive to Gulmarg (one of the best Ski resort destination in India). On arrival at Gulmarg, check in at your pre-booked hotel for an overnight stay.\r\n\"'),
(2255, 364, 'Gulmarg :', 'Skiing in Gulmarg Today, we will go for full day skiing activities. Later, return back to the hotel for an overnight stay.'),
(2256, 364, 'Gulmarg:', 'After breakfast in the morning, we will proceed for full day skiing activities. Later, return back to the hotel for an overnight stay.'),
(2257, 364, 'Gulmarg :', 'The day is fixed for enjoying skiing activities in Gulmarg. Later, return back to the hotel for an overnight stay.'),
(2258, 364, 'Gulmarg :', '\"In the morning after breakfast, we will go for full day skiing activities. Later, return back to the hotel for an overnight stay.\r\n\"'),
(2259, 364, 'Gulmarg :', 'Today, we will proceed for full day skiing activities. Later, return back to the hotel for an overnight stay.'),
(2260, 364, 'Gulmarg-Srinagar-Delhi:', 'In the morning after breakfast, we will take you to Srinagar airport, time to catch the flight for Delhi. On arrival at Delhi, we will take you to International airport, time to catch flight for onward destination.'),
(2261, 365, 'Arrive Srinagar', '\"Amarnath Helicopter Tour Meet on arrival at Srinagar Airport and transfer to Houseboat. Rest of the day free for leisure or do Shikara ride on The Dal Lake to enjoy the beauty that God has graced this city which is often compared to Heaven. There are lots of other interesting places around the Lake. Overnight at Houseboat.\r\n\"'),
(2262, 365, 'Srinagar - Sonamarg - Baltal – Holy Cave – Baltal - Sonamarg', '\"After breakfast drive to Sonmarg. On arrival check-in at hotel. After fresh-n-up drive to Baltal to board on a Helicopter to Holy Cave which will take you to Panchtarni (helicopter is subject to weather conditions). On arival at Panchtarni you have to trek approximately 6 kms to the holy caves. (You can hire palki / horses on direct payment). After Darshan trek back to Panchtarni for your helicopter ride back to Baltal where our driver will meet you and then drive to your hotel in Sonmarg. Overnight stay at hotel.\r\n\"'),
(2263, 365, 'Sonmarg – Srinagar', '\"Sonamarg (Meadow of Gold) – It is a place of enthralling beauty, lies in Sindh Valley, streamed with flowers, surrounded by mountains and perched at an altitude of 2690 m above sea level. Visited less frequently by tourists, it has as its backdrop, snowy mountains against a clear sky. It is a quiet alpine retreat surrounded with sycamore, silver birch, fir and pine trees and the last halt on the Kashmir side for the drive from Srinagar to Leh. It is also the base for some interesting treks to the high altitude of Himalayan Lakes. After having your lunch at local restaurant, feed your cameras with the picture of magnificent view of mountains. You can enjoy Horse ride at Sonmarg (Optional). Afternoon drive back from Sonmarg to Srinagar. Overnight stay at houseboat.\r\n\"'),
(2264, 365, 'Srinagar Drop', '\"After breakfast transfer to Airport for your onward destination.\r\n\"'),
(2265, 366, 'Arrive Jammu – Katra (45 kms)', 'Arrive Jammu train station and transfer you to hotel in Katra. Over night stay.'),
(2266, 366, 'Day Katra - Vaishno Devi - Katra', 'Today proceed to Vaishno Devi by walk and Pony. Take a holi Darshan of Vaishno Devi. Come back to katra for overnight stay.'),
(2267, 366, 'Katra - Jammu (45 kms)', 'After breakfast transfer you to the Katra.on arrival you will be transferred to Airport/train station for onward destination.'),
(2268, 367, 'Arrive Jammu – Katra - Mata Vaishno Devi Ji Darshanmata-vaisno-devi-tour', '\"Morning meet on arrival at Jammu Railway station and drive to Katra. On arrival at Katra check in at hotel. In the Afternoon at 1 ‘0’ clock transfer to Helipad to catch the chopper for Shanjichat. From here will start trek to Mata Vaishno Devi shrine. After Darshan back to Shanjichat to catch the chopper for Katra. On arrival transfer to hotel. Overnight at hotel.\r\n\"'),
(2269, 367, 'Katra – Shivkhori – Katra', '\"After early breakfast go for excursion to Shivkhori temple which is around 70 kms and takes 3 hrs each way to reach. Shivkhori means the cave of Lord Shiva. Along the way to Shivkhori. While driving to the holy place you will also visit two holy spots enroute. Aghar Jitto (6 kms from Katra) which is the shrine of revolutionary Baba Jitto. Next visit the shrine of Nau Deviyan (10 kms from Katra).shivkori-darshan\r\nOn reaching Shivkhori you will be dropped at the starting point of the yatra to the Shivling which is around 4 kms steep walk. The yatra and darshan can take anytime between 1.5 to 3 hours. After darshan return back to the starting point and transferred back to the hotel. Overnight stay at hotel.\r\n\"'),
(2270, 367, 'Katra – Jammu drop', '\"After Breakfast drive back to Jammu and transfer to Airport/Railway station for your onward destination.\r\n\"'),
(2271, 368, 'Arrive Jammu – Katra - Mata Vaishno Devi Ji Darshanmata-vaisno-devi-tour', '\"Morning meet on arrival at Jammu Railway station and drive to Katra. On arrival at Katra check in at hotel. In the Afternoon at 1 ‘0’ clock transfer to Helipad to catch the chopper for Shanjichat. From here will start trek to Mata Vaishno Devi shrine. After Darshan back to Shanjichat to catch the chopper for Katra. On arrival transfer to hotel. Overnight at hotel.\r\n\"'),
(2272, 368, 'Katra – Patnitop', '\"After breakfast drive to Patnitop (80 Kms). On arrival check-in at hotel. Evening visit Nag Temple & Padora Enclave. You may hire a pony to take a trip through the Pine trees and do not forget to take a camera along for memorable photography. Overnight stay at hotel.rpatnitop-tour\r\n\"'),
(2273, 368, 'Patnitop – Katra', '\"After breakfast half day sightseeing of Sanasar (Named after small local lakes, \'Sana\' & \'Sar\' are located 20 km west of Patnitop), Sanasar also called the mini Gulmarg and one of the remotest region of India, is a wonderful hill station in the state of Jammu and Kashmir and Nathatop- Nathatop is one of the most popular attraction of Patnitop. Nathatop will offer you a great view of Snow Coated Hills. Now a days Nathatop has been most popular for Paragliding and Hi Flying. \r\nAfternoon drive back to Katra. On arrival check-in at hotel. Overnight stay at hotel.\r\n\"'),
(2274, 368, 'Katra – Jammu drop', 'After breakfast drive back to Jammu. On arrival transfer to Airport/Railway station for your onward destination.'),
(2275, 370, 'Arrive Srinagar', '\"Meet on arrival at Srinagar Airport and transfer to Houseboat. Rest of the day free for leisure or do Shikara ride on The Dal Lake to enjoy the beauty that God has graced this city which is often compared to Heaven. There are lots of other interesting places around the Lake. Overnight at Houseboat.\r\n\"'),
(2276, 370, 'Srinagar - Sonamarg - Baltal – Holy Cave – Baltal - Sonamarg amarnath-yata', '\"After breakfast drive to Sonmarg. On arrival check-in at hotel. After fresh-n-up drive to Baltal to board on a Helicopter to Holy Cave which will take you to Panchtarni (helicopter is subject to weather conditions). On arival at Panchtarni you have to trek approximately 6 kms to the holy caves. (You can hire palki / horses on direct payment). After Darshan trek back to Panchtarni for your helicopter ride back to Baltal where our driver will meet you and then drive to your hotel in Sonmarg. Overnight stay at hotel.\r\n\"'),
